678
00:30:58,070 --> 00:30:58,880
Ask Mr. Lu.

679
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:00,160
Wasn't I trying to stop you?

680
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:01,440
Mr. Lu, say something.

681
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:03,920
This isn't Ye's fault.

682
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,550
It was my decision.

683
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:07,030
I'm sorry.

684
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,920
