685
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,240
What should we do now?

686
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:13,830
What else can we do? Now you're asking.

687
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:15,960
Who was so eager to take it on? "Me! Me!"

688
00:31:16,330 --> 00:31:17,880
